content:
Klipper makrolari Jinja2 template dili kullanir:

Degisken tanimlama:
{% set speed = params.SPEED|default(100)|int %}
{% set temp = printer.extruder.temperature %}

Kosul:
{% if printer.extruder.temperature > 200 %}
  G1 E10 F300  ; extrude
{% else %}
  M117 Sicaklik dusuk!
{% endif %}

Dongu:
{% for i in range(3) %}
  G0 X{10 + i*50} Y10 F6000
{% endfor %}

Printer nesneleri:
printer.extruder.temperature    # Mevcut sicaklik
printer.extruder.target         # Hedef sicaklik
printer.heater_bed.temperature  # Yatak sicakligi
printer.toolhead.position.z     # Z pozisyonu
printer.idle_timeout.state      # Idle durumu

Matematik:
{% set mid_x = printer.toolhead.axis_maximum.x / 2 %}

GET /printer/objects/query?extruder&heater_bed&toolhead
Klipper nesnelerinin durumunu sorgular.

Ornek:
curl 'http://localhost:7125/printer/objects/query?extruder=temperature,target&heater_bed=temperature,target&toolhead=position,homed_axes'

Yanit:
{
  "result": {
    "status": {
      "extruder": {"temperature": 205.3, "target": 210.0},
      "heater_bed": {"temperature": 59.8, "target": 60.0},
      "toolhead": {"position": [100, 100, 5, 0], "homed_axes": "xyz"}
    }
  }
}

Yaygin nesneler:
- extruder: temperature, target, pressure_advance
- heater_bed: temperature, target
- toolhead: position, homed_axes, max_velocity, max_accel
- print_stats: state, filename, total_duration, print_duration
- display_status: progress, message
- fan: speed

GET /server/temperature_store
Son 20 dakikalik sicaklik verisini dondurur (grafik icin).

Yanit (kisaltilmis):
{
  "result": {
    "extruder": {
      "temperatures": [20.1, 20.3, 25.5, ...],
      "targets": [0, 0, 210, ...],
      "powers": [0, 0, 1.0, ...]
    },
    "heater_bed": {
      "temperatures": [20.0, 20.1, ...],
      "targets": [0, 60, ...],
      "powers": [0, 1.0, ...]
    }
  }
}

Her dizi 1 saniyelik ornekleme ile ~1200 veri noktasi icerir.
Mainsail/Fluidd bu veriyi sicaklik grafigi icin kullanir.

Belirli sensor icin:
GET /server/temperature_store?include_monitors=false

curl http://localhost:7125/server/temperature_store

GET /server/history/list
Baski gecmisini listeler.

curl 'http://localhost:7125/server/history/list?limit=10&order=desc'

Yanit:
{
  "result": {
    "count": 150,
    "jobs": [
      {
        "job_id": "000042",
        "filename": "benchy.gcode",
        "status": "completed",
        "start_time": 1700000000.0,
        "end_time": 1700003600.0,
        "total_duration": 3600.0,
        "print_duration": 3200.0,
        "filament_used": 5000.5,
        "metadata": {...}
      }
    ]
  }
}

status degerleri: completed, cancelled, error, in_progress, klippy_shutdown

Istatistikler:
GET /server/history/totals
→ toplam baski sayisi, sure, filament kullanimi

WebSocket ile nesne degisikliklerini dinleme:

Subscribe istegi:
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "printer.objects.subscribe",
  "params": {
    "objects": {
      "extruder": ["temperature", "target"],
      "heater_bed": ["temperature", "target"],
      "print_stats": ["state", "filename"]
    }
  },
  "id": 2
}

Sonrasinda Moonraker otomatik bildirim gonderir:
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "notify_status_update",
  "params": [{
    "extruder": {"temperature": 210.5},
    "print_stats": {"state": "printing"}
  }, 1700000001.5]
}

Sadece degisen alanlar gonderilir (bandwidth tasarrufu).
Bildirim frekansi: ~250ms (4 Hz).

Diger bildirim turleri:
- notify_klippy_ready: Klipper hazir
- notify_klippy_shutdown: Klipper kapandi
- notify_gcode_response: G-code cikti mesajlari

Mainsail kurulum yontemleri:

KIAUH ile (onerilir):
cd ~
git clone https://github.com/dw-0/kiauh.git
./kiauh/kiauh.sh
→ 1) Install → 3) Mainsail

Manuel kurulum:
sudo apt install nginx
cd /home/klipper
mkdir mainsail
cd mainsail
wget -q https://github.com/mainsail-crew/mainsail/releases/latest/download/mainsail.zip
unzip mainsail.zip

Nginx config (/etc/nginx/sites-available/mainsail):
server {
  listen 80 default_server;
  root /home/klipper/mainsail;
  index index.html;
  location /websocket { proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:7125; ... }
  location /printer { proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:7125; ... }
  location /server { proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:7125; ... }
}

Guncelleme: Moonraker update_manager ile otomatik veya KIAUH ile.
